{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Border Pioneer is a pixel art city-building game that combines survival and defense elements. Fresh from the academy, you must prove your worth by venturing into the frontiers. Face local dangers, manage resources, construct towns, and expand the kingdom's borders into uncharted territories!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Build Your Village</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346410/extras/1.gif?t=1739382646\" /><strong>Build Your Town from Scratch</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Transform barren lands into bustling settlements! Start with basic structures and gradually unlock new buildings and units as you progress.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Collect And Expand Your Deck!</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346410/extras/2.gif?t=1739382646\" /><strong>Build Your Deck!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose from over 200 unique cards to construct your perfect deck. Use your cards with skill and timing to overcome challenges and build your town efficiently.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> <br><strong>Fend Off Enemy Assaults!</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346410/extras/3.gif?t=1739382646\" /><strong>Defend Against Relentless Threats</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">At the end of each month, enemies will attempt to destroy the town you so carefully built! Fortify your defenses and repel increasingly powerful waves of attackers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Prove Your Worth as a Pioneer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Manage resources, plan your town's layout, and make crucial decisions to ensure your town's survival and growth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Border Pioneer offers a unique blend of city-building strategy and defensive gameplay. Can you tame the wild frontier and become the world\u2019s most legendary pioneer?</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"I'm ready","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2346410/b5d6481b8287785e08dfc69403a30ed32c9e7392.jpg"},{"name":"You gotta fall to learn to fly","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2346410/b53b6b39b733477b7f8ec849d103ef120dacceb4.jpg"},{"name":"It takes two to tango","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2346410/f2abe772a6aead4abb12ef22548fa874e0d6fe44.jpg"},{"name":"I'm stuffed","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2346410/5dd9a836988ce906039a00e79ea5319b0ab9626f.jpg"},{"name":"Wall it all up","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2346410/35b24f98feec786a0c4fb2f8a25b20c68cfe0ebf.jpg"},{"name":"Packed to the rafters","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2346410/7259e6b76d4d9524aa3f38d23b638e2db8810489.jpg"},{"name":"Capitalism","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2346410/a45182e023a884de6784d39c90cf7da2f1ef30a0.jpg"},{"name":"Don't you ever upgrade?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2346410/330b7eaf5d842f58f3ffab22a776abf9fecc24ec.jpg"},{"name":"You scared me","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2346410/8971396d135b952e909a9273d2634aa7cb754e40.jpg"},{"name":"Snatch up a small bargain","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2346410/85b01da13b47a0cf2b93ffef12843869d4143206.jpg"}],"total":31},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346410/page_bg_generated_v6b